[Civil No. 825.] In the Matter of the Application of W. H. CHAPMAN for a Writ of Certiorari to the Board of Supervisors of the County of Graham, Territory of Arizona. Herring & Mitchell, for Petitioner. Hereford & Hazzard, for W. H. Settle. March 20, 1903.

ORIGINAL PROCEEDING.

Judgment entered annulling proceedings of the board.
